{"tha-ap96:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap96:0.2":"Sudhavagga ","tha-ap96:0.3":"Sucidayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap96:1.1":"“Kammaroham pure asim, ","tha-ap96:1.2":"bandhumayam puruttame; ","tha-ap96:1.3":"Sucidanam maya dinnam, ","tha-ap96:1.4":"vipassissa mahesino. ","tha-ap96:2.1":"Vajiraggasamam nanam, ","tha-ap96:2.2":"hoti kammena tadisam; ","tha-ap96:2.3":"Viragomhi vimuttomhi, ","tha-ap96:2.4":"pattomhi asavakkhayam. ","tha-ap96:3.1":"Atite ca bhave sabbe, ","tha-ap96:3.2":"vattamane canagate; ","tha-ap96:3.3":"Nanena vicinim sabbam, ","tha-ap96:3.4":"sucidanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap96:4.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap96:4.2":"sattasum vajiravhaya; ","tha-ap96:4.3":"Sattaratanasampanna, ","tha-ap96:4.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap96:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap96:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap96:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap96:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sucidayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap96:7.1":"Sucidayakattherassapadanam catuttham. "}